OL,6,Fcan be nerve inducing at the best of
OL,7,Ftimes, but with almost three quarters
OL,8,Fof maternity units across the North
OL,9,FEast and North Yorkshire now
OL,10,Fsubstandard, there are calls for
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,FSince 2022, the has re-inspected
OL,14,Fmaternity units across the country,
OL,15,Fand the results paint a picture of
OL,16,Fdeclining care.
