OL,6,FIn England almost half of maternity
OL,7,Fservices are substandard (49%). Of 15
OL,8,Funits in the North East and North
OL,9,FYorkshire that have been re-inspected
OL,10,Fso far, almost 3 quarters are failing
OL,11,F(73%).
OL,13,F, , Scarborough and York were in the
OL,14,Flatest round of visits.
OL,16,FThe RVI in Newcastle, James Cook
OL,17,FHospital in Middlesbrough and
OL,18,FSunderland Royal are among the other
OL,19,Flocal hospitals told to make
OL,20,Fimprovements.
