OL,3,CAlmost three quarters of maternity
OL,4,Cunits in the region currently failing
OL,6,FIn their state of care report, the CQC
OL,7,Fsaid the overarching picture is one of
OL,8,Fa service and staff under huge
OL,9,Fpressure.
OL,11,FOne of those who felt their level of
OL,12,Fcare fell short, was Philippa Elliot
OL,13,Ffrom Darlington. Her waters broke at
OL,14,Fjust 19 weeks pregnant.
OL,16,FShe was admitted to Darlington
OL,17,FMemorial Hospital, but told she
OL,18,Fcouldn't have a scan, as no ultrasound
OL,19,Fspecialists on shift.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
