OL,3,CAlmost three quarters of maternity
OL,4,Cunits in the region currently failing
OL,6,FShe was left for days, not knowing if
OL,7,Fher baby was alive.
OL,9,FPhilippa said: "It was only on day
OL,10,Fthree, when I was about to be
OL,11,Fdischarged that one of the doctors
OL,12,Fcame and asked 'has anybody scanned
OL,13,Fyou?' and I said 'no, apparently you
OL,14,Fhaven't got any ultrasound specialists
OL,15,Fin over the weekend'.
OL,17,F"The doctor said that he is not a
OL,18,Fspecialist but could scan me and tell
OL,19,Fme if there was fluid. He scanned,
OL,20,Fthere was fluid there so we left and
OL,21,Ftransferred care to James Cook."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
