OL,6,F"It was terrifying. I don't think I've
OL,7,Fever cried as much as I did in those
OL,8,Fthree days. It was awful. At that
OL,9,Fpoint, I didn't even know if she was
OL,10,Fstill alive."
OL,12,FThe advice from doctors at Darlington
OL,13,FMemorial Hospital, was to terminate
OL,14,Fthe pregnancy. Reluctant to give up
OL,15,Fhope, Philippa and her husband
OL,16,Fresearched alternative options.
OL,18,FThey found NHS guidelines that
OL,19,Fsuggested there are cases where, with
OL,20,Fclose monitoring, pregnancies can
OL,21,Fcontinue, with a positive outcome.
