OL,6,FShe said: "I can't imagine how I would
OL,7,Ffeel now if I had terminated and then
OL,8,Frealised it might have been ok."
OL,10,FFollowing this experience at
OL,11,FDarlington, Philippa transferred to
OL,12,FJames Cook in Middlesbrough. Under
OL,13,Ftheir care, she carried Baby Ivy Hope
OL,14,Funtil 28 weeks.
OL,16,FShe was born premature, but healthy.
OL,18,FNoel Scanlon, Executive Director of
OL,19,FNursing and Midwifery at County Durham
OL,20,Fand Darlington NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,21,Fsaid:
