OL,6,F"We are committed to providing high
OL,7,Fquality, compassionate care to all
OL,8,Fwomen and families. We sincerely
OL,9,Fapologise to any family who has felt
OL,10,Flet down by their experience in our
OL,11,Fcare and we take these matters
OL,12,Fseriously.
OL,14,F"We recognise that our maternity
OL,15,Fservices are facing pressures and have
OL,16,Fbeen open and transparent in
OL,17,Facknowledging these but also in
OL,18,Fsharing our commitment to continuous
OL,19,Fimprovement."
