OL,6,FThe Trust says it has taken steps to
OL,7,Fmake improvements, to ensure a high
OL,8,Flevel of care is provided to all
OL,9,Fpatients.
OL,11,FThe statement went on to say: "Over
OL,12,Fthe past 12 months, we have worked
OL,13,Fclosely with our dedicated teams to
OL,14,Fmake many improvements. In particular,
OL,15,Fwe continue to actively recruit to
OL,16,Fstaffing vacancies and recently
OL,17,Fwelcomed a new Director of Midwifery
OL,18,Fto the Trust and a second Head of
OL,19,FMidwifery.
