OL,6,F"We are dedicated to listening,
OL,7,Flearning, and continually improving
OL,8,Fthe quality of care and experience we
OL,9,Fare offering our women and families."
OL,11,FDr Bill Kirkup has led inquiries into
OL,12,Fservices elsewhere in the country,
OL,13,Fincluding Jimmy Savile's involvement
OL,14,Fat Broadmoor Hospital and failings at
OL,15,FMorecambe Bay Maternity Services.
OL,17,FHe says the latest CQC ratings are
OL,18,Ffurther proof that there are systemic
OL,19,Fissues.
