OL,6,FDr Kirkup said: "There are problems
OL,7,Fparticularly with professional
OL,8,Fculture, around compassion and
OL,9,Flistening and team working and there
OL,10,Fare problems around the reaction that
OL,11,Fpeople have where there is a serious
OL,12,Fsafety incident. It needs looking at,
OL,13,Fit needs investigating.
OL,15,F"Of course mistakes happen but the
OL,16,Fthings shouldn't keep happening year
OL,17,Fafter year. These are widespread
OL,18,Fproblems and we need to work on how we
OL,19,Fcan change that."
